  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK732">
<l>perumporuḷāṟ peṭṭakka tākiyarum kēṭṭā</l>
<l>lāṟṟa viḷaivatu nāṭu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>A kingdom is that which is desire for its immense wealth, and which grows greatly in prosperity, being free from destructive causes.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
